label: black cohosh supplement
Equivalence axiom: 'dietary supplement, botanical' and 'derives from' some (root and 'part of' some 'Actaea racemosa')
definition: A botanical dietary supplement composed primarily of the root or root extract of the Actaea racemosa plant.
black bugbane supplement|black snakeroot supplement|Cimicifuga racemosa supplement
comment: Black cohosh supplementation has been used in functional medicine for management of menopausal symptoms.
